brief_summary: This is a three-year study to determine if estrogens can prevent memory loss and Alzheimer's disease in women with a family history of Alzheimer's disease.
eligibility_criteria: Inclusion Criteria: - Healthy women 65 or older with a family history of memory problems not currently on estrogen. Exclusion Criteria: - Significant neurological impairment - Current estrogen use - History of breast cancer
